<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #d32f2f;
      color: white;
      padding: 15px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 4px 4px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-top: none;
      border-radius: 0 0 4px 4px;
    }
    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin: 20px 0;
      background-color: #fff;
    }
    th, td {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 12px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    th {
      background-color: #f2f2f2;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    tr:nth-child(even) {
      background-color: #fafafa;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>⚠️ Overdue Reports Alert</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello,</p>
      <p>The following parts do not have completed reports for today (<strong>{{date}}</strong>). Please ensure these are completed as soon as possible.</p>
      
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Part Number</th>
            <th>Part Name</th>
            <th>Missing Report Type</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          {{#each alerts}}
          <tr>
            <td><strong>{{partNumber}}</strong></td>
            <td>{{partName}}</td>
            <td><span style="color: #d32f2f;">{{missingType}}</span></td>
          </tr>
          {{/each}}
        </tbody>
      </table>
      
      <p>Please log in to the IRMS system and complete the pending reports.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated message from the IRMS System. Please do not reply.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
